Title: Part 12: The Spider Shelob
Text:
Gollum led to the secret tunnel at Minas Morgul.
I don't know if I can trust him, but I have no other choice.

>>(Kill the spider Shelob, it is at the exit of the tunnel)<<
CompleteText:
Gollum has betrayed us!
It was a trap and a giant spider appeared!

Luckily I was able to defeat it after a hard fight.
There is no trace of Gollum. I should move on quickly.

Only it will be difficult to get past the old watchtower Cirith Ungol.
I should take a look there first!
